She was in my house. She
made a not so veiled threat.

159
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:33,820
我妈和妹妹必须严加保护
I want extra security
around my mother and sister.

160
00:10:33,820 --> 00:10:36,110
- 早就想到了 兄弟
- 谢谢
- Way ahead of you,man.
- Thank you.

161
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:39,600
- 这是我的工作
- 别这种口气
- It's my job.
- For not saying,"I told you so."

162
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,490
长夜漫漫
Night's young.

163
00:10:46,530 --> 00:10:49,410
你去哪了 俱乐部四小时后就开张了
Where you been? The
club opens in four hours.

164
00:10:49,410 --> 00:10:52,340
- 我在处理供应商的事情
- 你没有
- I've been dealing with the vendors.
- No,you haven't.

165
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:57,470
Tommy 我们得谈谈
Tommy... We need to talk.

166
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:02,210
我很抱歉
I'm sorry,all right.

167
00:11:02,210 --> 00:11:06,730
我不说是为了保护身边的人
But I kept this a secret to protect
the people that are closest to me.

168
00:11:06,730 --> 00:11:09,630
你以为我关心这个吗
Do you think that's what I care about?

169
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:12,820
是因为我被伤到了吗
What,that my feelings are hurt?

170
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:18,190
你是凶手 是杀人犯
You're a murderer. A killer.

171
00:11:18,190 --> 00:11:22,990
你是我最好的朋友
可我现在完全不认识你了
You were my best friend in life, but
now it's like I don't even know you.

172
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:25,890
你说得对 我变了
You're right. I've changed.

173
00:11:25,890 --> 00:11:28,060
兄弟 现在我可以向你解释
Listen,buddy,now I can explain to you.

174
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:30,640
我可以解释为什么...
I can explain to
you how and why--

175
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:33,160
有意义吗
What'd be the point?

176
00:11:33,700 --> 00:11:36,680
反正我不会再信你
I wouldn't believe a word of it,anyway.

177
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:50,710
其中一枚导弹的有效射程是2400公里
One of those missiles has an effective
range of up to 2,400 kilometers.

178
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:55,310
查清Fyers的阴谋前 咱俩哪儿也不去
We're not going anywhere until we
figure out what Fyers is planning.

179
00:11:57,310 --> 00:12:00,400
我猜 他要炸掉什么吧
Wild guess? He's planning
on blowing something up.

180
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:04,400
用那枚导弹 大材小用
Well,one of those could
do the job. But this?

181
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:07,570
这是发动战争的征兆
This is about starting a war.

182
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:10,950
- 跟谁打
- 有什么关系
- With who?
- What does it matter?

183
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:16,460
我们得阻止Fyers涂炭生灵
We have to stop Fyers before he
kills thousands of innocent people.

184
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:17,760
下面重兵集结呢
There are tons of soldiers down there.

185
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:19,280
即使我俩把他们都撂倒
Even if we get through all of them,

186
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:22,870
也没法偷走整套导弹发射器
we can't just steal a
whole missile launcher.

187
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:31,150
谁说要偷了
Well,who said anything
about stealing it?

188
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:36,520
那要干嘛 伏击
So what's the plan? Ambush?

189
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:40,140
不行 一次性得搞定6个人 
其中肯定会有人呼叫援助
It's impossible. We can't take out all
six without one radioing for back up.

190
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:43,590
如果能把那些兵聚集在一起就好了
It'd be good if we could get
all the soldiers in one place.

191
00:12:47,650 --> 00:12:49,400
不错
You're right.

192
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:57,120
破玩意儿
*****

193
00:13:00,010 --> 00:13:01,710
订书机得罪你了
What'd the stapler ever do to you?

194
00:13:01,710 --> 00:13:05,610
干嘛 Laurel 我忙着呢
帽衫侠的女友回来了
What is it,Laurel? I'm busy.
The Hood's girlfriend is back.

195
00:13:05,610 --> 00:13:09,380
爸 早上的事 我很抱歉
Dad,I'm sorry about this morning.

196
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:12,240
可如果我据实以告
But if I told you the
real reason to come see me,

197
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,340
你根本不会来见我
you wouldn't have shown up.

198
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:15,720
你说得太对了
You're damn right I wouldn't.

199
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:20,350
你妈说Sarah还活在奇幻岛上
So you really believe this
garbage your mother's selling

200
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:23,660
你真相信这种胡话
about Sarah being
alive on fantasy island?

201
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:26,850
不
I mean,no.

202
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:32,060
但看一看妈妈的发现 也没什么坏处啊
But what would it hurt to take a
look at everything that mom found?

203
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:34,850
即使只是让她面对现实
Even if it's just to set her straight.

204
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:36,720
Laurel 你知不知道我花了多久
Laurel,you know how
long it's taken for me

205
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:40,940
才使自己不要每天一早就想起Sarah
to get to a place where Sarah isn't the
first thing I think about every morning?

206
00:13:40,940 --> 00:13:42,850
爸...
Dad...

207
00:13:49,110 --> 00:13:52,560
转告你妈 我不做任何承诺
Tell your mom I'm not
making any promises.

208
00:14:19,660 --> 00:14:21,340
敬翡翠
To Verdant.

209
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:25,440
我没有一直支持这个项目
I know I haven't always been
supportive of this venture,

210
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:30,550
但我必须承认 这个夜店很赞
but I have to admit this nightclub
is quite an accomplishment.

211
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:34,510
我以你为傲 你父亲肯定也一样
I'm proud of you. Your
father would be,too.

212
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:35,520
谢谢
***

213
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:39,040
恭喜 Ollie 这儿也不是很糟啦
Yeah,congratulations,Ollie.
The club doesn't totally suck.

214
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:43,200
过奖 飞毛腿 谢谢大家来捧场
Thanks,Speedy. Thank you very
much,all of you,for coming.

215
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:53,400
你在这儿呢
There you are.

216
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:58,270
这地方真棒 我为你和Ollie自豪
This place is amazing. I'm
so proud of you and Ollie.

217
00:14:58,580 --> 00:15:00,280
谢谢
Thanks.

218
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:04,690
- 你没事吧
- 我挺好
- Is everything ok?
- I'm great.

219
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,960
早餐真是场灾难
Well,breakfast was a disaster.

220
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:11,380
早餐 和我父母
Breakfast? With my parents?

221
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:14,440
对 今早的事
Right. That was this morning.

222
00:15:16,330 --> 00:15:17,580
对不起
Sorry.

223
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:22,230
你确定没事吗 你看起来心不在焉的
Are you sure everything's ok?
Because you seem completely off.

224
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:24,680
没事 真的
I'm fine. I promise.

225
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:27,090
Tommy Tommy 你打给Roy了吗
Tommy! Tommy. Did you call Roy yet?

226
00:15:27,090 --> 00:15:30,080
我给他留言了 他明天来上班
I left him a message.
He starts tomorrow.

227
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:34,990
我得去办公室看看
Which reminds me,I have to
go check in with the office.

228
00:15:34,990 --> 00:15:36,330
失陪了
Excuse me.

229
00:15:36,820 --> 00:15:41,420
嘿 Tommy 还记得我吗
Hey,Tommy. Remember me?

230
00:16:06,850 --> 00:16:09,870
- Queen先生 打扰你一下
- 没关系 反正我又不会跳舞
- Sorry to bother you,Mr. Queen.
- Your timing is perfect. I can't dance.

231
00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:11,790
他们说这个很紧急
They said it was urgent.

232
00:16:12,780 --> 00:16:14,410
<i>楼下见 立刻--Dig</i>
<i>meet**</i>

233
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:17,770
- 你还好吧
- 嗯 水晶香槟快喝完了
- You ok?
- Yeah. We ran out of Cristal.

234
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:20,080
- 我去去就回
- 好
- I'll be right back.
- Ok.

235
00:16:23,730 --> 00:16:25,280
Dig
Dig?

236
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:31,920
放开他 跟他无关
Let him go. He has
nothing to do with this.

237
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:35,420
我说过 Oliver 我警告过你
I told you. Oliver,I warned you.

238
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:37,630
Helena 别这样
Helena! This isn't you.

239
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:41,210
我父亲是个歹徒 凶手
My father is a mobster and a murderer.

240
00:16:41,210 --> 00:16:44,320
好像你没杀过人似的
It is not like you haven't
killed men like that before!

241
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:48,050
我教过你 避免杀戮而达到目的
And I tried to teach you to obtain
your objective without killing!

242
00:16:48,050 --> 00:16:50,080
通过制约别人
By applying leverage.

243
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:53,500
通过利用别人的弱点
By exploiting someone's weakness.

244
00:16:57,810 --> 00:17:03,030
上面那一屋子人 我都可以抓来制约你
There is a whole club full of
leverage above our heads right now.

245
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:05,060
求你了
Please.

246
00:17:05,060 --> 00:17:08,030
Oliver 别逼我做出让我们都后悔的事
Oliver,don't make me do something
that both of us will regret.

247
00:17:08,030 --> 00:17:13,970
好 你赢了 我会帮你 放开他
Ok! Ok. You win. I'll
help you. Let him go.

248
00:17:13,970 --> 00:17:17,780
放 开 他
Let... Him... Go!

249
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:35,320
- 别提那事
- 好
- Don't say it.
- Ok.

250
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:38,280
那就谈谈Helena吧
Then let's talk about Helena.

251
00:17:40,010 --> 00:17:42,800
Oliver 如果你不是还对她有感觉的话
Oliver,if you didn't still
have feelings for this girl,

252
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:44,430
你会想出别的解决之道
you would have thought
of a different solution

253
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:46,650
而不会受她威胁去杀人
than letting her extort
you into killing someone.

254
00:17:46,650 --> 00:17:48,660
你想要我怎么做
So what do you want me to do?

255
00:17:49,630 --> 00:17:50,810
杀掉她吗
You want me to kill her?

256
00:17:50,810 --> 00:17:52,120
你是看她长得漂亮
I think you would have a long time ago

257
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:54,860
要不你早就杀她了
if she looked like me
instead of the T-Mobile girl.

258
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:58,080
- 她是个无情的杀手 Oliver
- 她并不邪恶
- She's a stone cold killer,Oliver.
- She's not evil.

259
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:02,460
她父亲冷血地杀掉她未婚夫 她迷茫了
She's been lost since her father
killed her fiancé in cold blood.

260
00:18:02,460 --> 00:18:04,780
你想冷眼旁观地说
And are you going to sit there

261
00:18:04,780 --> 00:18:08,330
你不懂得复仇的欲望吗
and tell me that you don't know
what it's like to want revenge?

262
00:18:08,330 --> 00:18:11,410
换了是你 会怎么做
What would you do? Hmm?

263
00:18:11,410 --> 00:18:14,200
如果Floyd Lawton站在那儿
If Floyd Lawton was
standing right there?

264
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:17,950
反正不会威胁你去杀他
Nothing that will involve
blackmailing you into hunting him down.

265
00:18:17,950 --> 00:18:23,170
你说对了 我是下不了手杀她
You're right. Ok? I can't kill her.

266
00:18:23,170 --> 00:18:27,520
我也不能冒着泄露身份的风险 
把她交给警察
And I can't take her to the police
and risk her exposing all of this.

267
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:31,160
但至少 如果我参与其中 我能控制她
But at least,if I'm involved,I
can contain her,all right?

268
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:34,490
我可以最大程度减少间接损害
I can minimize the collateral damage.

269
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:38,140
抱歉 我打扰你们了吗
Sorry,am I... interrupting something?

270
00:18:38,140 --> 00:18:41,450
我们正谈起你
We were just... talking about you.

271
00:18:41,450 --> 00:18:43,700
以前觉得你很不在乎我
And here I thought you
didn't care much for me.

272
00:18:43,700 --> 00:18:45,440
一如既往
Still don't.

273
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:47,000
我还没找到
I haven't been able to
locate the safe house

274
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,830
FBI软禁你父亲的地方
where the FBI is keeping your father.

275
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:52,310
我能帮忙 我超想黑进FBI的安全系统
I can help with that. I've been dying
to hack into the FBI security system.

276
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:54,960
出去 出去
Get out. Get out.

277
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:58,010
这是私事 Felicity 请离开
This is a private
thing,Felicity. Please.

278
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:01,270
好吧
Ok.

279
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:04,260
那么 再见
See ya,I guess...

280
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:11,130
你到底有多少女朋友
How many girlfriends
do you have,exactly?

281
00:19:11,130 --> 00:19:14,500
如我所说 我们没查到软禁地址
Like I said... We don't
know where the safe house is.

282
00:19:14,500 --> 00:19:17,000
我们只知道今晚
What we do know is that the Marshall
service is taking your father

283
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:19,990
法警要带你父亲去司法部的听证会
to a hearing at the
Justice Department tonight.

284
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:24,010
有个问题 Helena
There's a problem... Helena.

285
00:19:24,010 --> 00:19:27,700
有两辆车 其中一辆是诱饵
There are two vans. And
one of them's a decoy.

286
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:29,800
我们也有两个人啊
Well,it's a good thing
there's two of us,then.

287
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:31,550
现在取消行动 为时未晚
It's not too late to call this off.

288
00:19:31,550 --> 00:19:34,060
你了解我的
I think you know me better than that.

289
00:19:34,060 --> 00:19:36,550
我不让他坐牢
I don't take prisoners.

290
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:48,220
我巡视的时候发现这家伙
I found an intruder while I
was circling the perimeter.

291
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:55,520
是Wilson
It's Wilson.

292
00:19:56,430 --> 00:19:58,650
你杀了我好几个朋友 混蛋
You killed a few of my
friends,you son of a bitch.

293
00:19:58,650 --> 00:20:01,080
那我再杀几个
And I'm going to kill a few more.

294
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:16,480
我先跟我们的律师谈谈 
然后叫他们给你回电
I'll talk to one of our lawyers
and have them call you right back.

295
00:20:17,710 --> 00:20:19,600
刮胡子弄伤了
Cut yourself shaving?

296
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:24,960
- 能聊会儿吗
- 可以
- You got a minute?
- Sure.

297
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:29,900
- Roy第一天表现如何
- 那小子没来
- How was Roy's first day?
- Kid never showed.

298
00:20:32,710 --> 00:20:36,700
我过来是想为昨晚的事道歉
I just,uh,I came by to
apologize for last night.

299
00:20:36,930 --> 00:20:40,110
比起道歉 我更想知道实情
Instead of an apology,why
don't you try the truth?

300
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,850
你可以从腕伤谈起
You can start with your wrist.

301
00:20:41,850 --> 00:20:45,030
我在夜店跟一个搅局的打了一架
I got into a fight with
a blender at the club.

302
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:47,540
挺二的
It was stupid.

303
00:20:47,540 --> 00:20:50,520
我以为你会说实话
I thought I asked for the truth.

304
00:20:51,890 --> 00:20:55,650
肯定发生什么事了 为什么不告诉我
I know something's up. Why won't
you tell me what's going on?

305
00:20:57,360 --> 00:21:00,890
- 我不能说
- 为什么
- Because I can't.
- Why not?

306
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:06,330
这个我也不能说 我真希望可以告诉你
I can't tell you that,either.
I wish that I could.

307
00:21:06,330 --> 00:21:08,930
Laurel 对不起
Laurel,I'm sorry.

308
00:21:10,060 --> 00:21:11,920
我也是
So am I.

309
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,970
现在我真的很需要你 Tommy
I really need you right now,Tommy.

310
00:21:14,970 --> 00:21:17,620
我妈跑来跟我说我姐没死
My mother shows up saying my
dead sister is still alive,

311
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:20,290
我听信了她 我爸因此发飙了
and my father is furious with me
that I'm even listening to her.

312
00:21:20,290 --> 00:21:23,190
我真不知该信谁了
And I don't know who to believe.

313
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:25,930
- 我快崩溃了
- 我在你身边呢
- I feel like I'm falling apart.
- I'm still here for you.

314
00:21:25,930 --> 00:21:28,900
不 你没有 你人在心不在
No. You're not. You're
a million miles away,

315
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:32,330
最糟的是 我不知这是为何
and the worst part is,I
don't even know why.

316
00:21:34,110 --> 00:21:35,600
对不起
I'm sorry.

317
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:47,510
跟踪我哈
Wow. Stalker much?

318
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:49,810
我给你找了份工作 你却没来上班
You didn't show up
for the job I got you.

319
00:21:49,810 --> 00:21:52,510
我改主意了 不想帮你哥停宾利车
Yeah,I had second thoughts about
parking your brother's Bentley.

320
00:21:52,510 --> 00:21:54,620
怎么 当泊车的跌份儿吗
What,being a valet is beneath you?

321
00:21:54,620 --> 00:21:57,320
不 接受富家女的施舍才跌份儿
No,but accepting charity
from some rich girl is.

322
00:21:57,320 --> 00:22:00,910
我是有钱人 为什么会让你如此反感
Why are you so obsessed with
the fact that I have money?

323
00:22:00,910 --> 00:22:02,700
金钱不是万能的
You know,money isn't everything.

324
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:05,630
果然是有钱人的口吻
Spoken like someone who's got it.

