504
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:50,410
M. HALL警探
<i>det**</i>

505
00:38:57,120 --> 00:39:01,980
- 你在清理你的桌子吗
- 不 朋友的
- Are you cleaning out your desk?
- No. A friend's.

506
00:39:03,500 --> 00:39:05,830
你找我
You asked to see me.

507
00:39:06,970 --> 00:39:09,510
- 坐吧
- 好
- Why don't you take a seat.
- Ok.

508
00:39:22,740 --> 00:39:26,030
我准备好听你说了
I'm ready to listen now.

509
00:39:29,890 --> 00:39:31,870
谢谢
Thank you.

510
00:39:41,390 --> 00:39:45,880
我听说了McKenna的事 你还好吗
I,uh,heard about McKenna. You ok?

511
00:39:46,690 --> 00:39:48,880
不太好
Not really.

512
00:39:50,930 --> 00:39:54,310
听着 我知道我最近很混蛋
Look,I know that I
have been a jerk lately.

513
00:39:54,310 --> 00:40:00,090
我只是不明白
你怎么能对我隐瞒这个大秘密
I just couldn't understand how you
could keep such a huge secret from me.

514
00:40:00,090 --> 00:40:05,480
但我从没想过你为此所牺牲的
But I-- I never considered
the toll it must take on you.

515
00:40:06,830 --> 00:40:11,440
对亲近的人说谎
Lying to the people
that are closest to me.

516
00:40:12,290 --> 00:40:14,700
这是最难的
It's the hardest part.

517
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:16,480
我明白
I get that.

518
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:21,850
我之前错了...
I was wrong...

519
00:40:21,850 --> 00:40:25,340
以为我可以有双重身份
to think that I could have it both ways;

520
00:40:25,340 --> 00:40:29,120
能做我要做的
that I could do what I do

521
00:40:29,120 --> 00:40:32,290
还能过正常的生活
and still have a normal life.

522
00:40:34,150 --> 00:40:35,490
不为人所知
With anyone.

523
00:40:35,490 --> 00:40:40,420
除非孑身一人 不然不会开心
Except if you're alone,you're
never going to be happy.

524
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:43,600
或许不是这样
Maybe not.

525
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:49,870
但我开心 不是最重要的事
But me being happy isn't
what's important right now.

526
00:40:54,020 --> 00:40:57,770
你的计划 你做主
Your plan,your call.

527
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,960
Fyers
Fyers.

528
00:41:04,430 --> 00:41:08,150
Queen先生 我知道你会联系我
Mr. Queen. I thought I
might be hearing from you.

529
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:11,120
电路板在我们手里
We have the circuit board.

530
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:13,470
你这是自掘坟墓
You're making a grave mistake.

531
00:41:13,470 --> 00:41:16,620
我的人正在搜查这座岛
My men are scouring the
island for you as we speak.

532
00:41:16,620 --> 00:41:20,310
他们找到你 会杀了你
And when they find
you,they will kill you.

533
00:41:20,310 --> 00:41:23,070
恐怕是慢慢折磨死
Very slowly,I'm afraid.

534
00:41:23,070 --> 00:41:25,510
如果你的人杀了我们
你就别想拿到电路板了
If your men kill us,then you'll
never find the circuit board.

535
00:41:25,510 --> 00:41:27,990
在那之后 你我都明白
And after that,we both know
that all you'll be left with

536
00:41:27,990 --> 00:41:31,060
你手中就只有一团废铁
is a really ugly piece of modern art.

537
00:41:33,670 --> 00:41:36,280
你想怎样
What do you propose?

538
00:41:36,640 --> 00:41:38,070
做笔交易
A trade.

539
00:41:38,070 --> 00:41:42,440
明白了 想拿什么交换
I see. And what do you want in exchange?

540
00:41:47,310 --> 00:41:49,340
离岛
I want a way off the island.

